import React from "react"
import { Card } from "react-bootstrap"
import '../styles/Product.css'

export default function Product(){

    return (
        <Card>
            
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Text>
                    Product Name
                </Card.Text>

            </Card.Body>
           <Card.Footer>
                <Card.Title>$$$</Card.Title>
                <Card.Text>$$$</Card.Text>
           </Card.Footer>
        </Card>
    )
}
